00:36:12.480 --> 00:36:15.870
So how do I find c_3?

00:36:15.870 --> 00:36:17.070
Let me slow down a second.

00:36:17.070 --> 00:36:18.210
How to find c_3?

00:36:22.210 --> 00:36:27.430
Multiply both sides by what?

00:36:27.430 --> 00:36:31.680
